---
layout: layouts/inner.njk
title: News
permalink: /news/
eyebrow:
  en: Latest News
  vi: Tin tức
  zh: 最新资讯
heading:
  en: Insights That Drive Progress.
  vi: Thông tin tạo nên giá trị.
  zh: 以洞察驱动进步。
lead:
  en: Stay updated with projects, innovations, sustainability initiatives and industry developments.
  vi: Cập nhật dự án, hoạt động và xu hướng mới nhất từ Nam Việt.
  zh: 了解我们最新的项目、创新与行业动态。
---

<div class="news__grid">
  {% for post in collections.news %}
  <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="ncard">
    <div class="ncard__media"><img src="{{ post.data.image | url }}" alt="" loading="lazy"></div>
    <span class="ncard__cat">
      <span class="lang en">{{ post.data.category.en }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ post.data.category.vi }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ post.data.category.zh }}</span>
    </span>
    <h3>
      <span class="lang en">{{ post.data.title.en }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ post.data.title.vi }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ post.data.title.zh }}</span>
    </h3>
    <span class="ncard__more">
      <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.readMore }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.readMore }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.readMore }}</span> →
    </span>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
<p class="page-actions">
  <a class="rss-link" href="{{ '/news/feed.xml' | url }}">
    <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.rssFeed }}</span>
    <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.rssFeed }}</span>
    <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.rssFeed }}</span>
  </a>
</p>
